A police officer was arrested on Wednesday for using his firearm while drunk on Mombasa- Nairobi highway.The cop, who works at one the SGR sites, was arrested at Ndi in Taita Taveta county, disarmed and locked up in Voi police station.Tsavo National Park police boss Julius Cheptai said the officer was involved in a fight with an officer from the Kenya Wildlife Services (KWS)."He ended up shooting in the air oblivious of the danger he posed to the people at the site. No one was injured during the incident," Cheptai said.